ai os log:
    schema:
        have a rich schema having metadatas 
        have timestamps of actions done
        short summary what is done in this stage, then indexing with the ai os main database to have sense how things processed 
        even errors be captured 
    It would be used as a visuals of performance measuring of the ai os system 
    Have a skill to manage the log schema, log insertion and more. 
    


